    "We also refer to Pessach and Shmueli (2022); Hort et al. (2022); Mehrabi et al. (2021); Ashurst and Weller (2023) and to Fabris et al. (2022); Quy et al. (2022), respectively, for surveys of the techniques and of the experimental datasets commonly used in the field.",
    "Several off-the-shelf software libraries are available to practitioners, expanding at a fast pace.",
